All Classes

  • All Classes Interface Summary Class Summary Enum Summary Exception Summary 
    Class Description
    Aircraft
    Represents an aircraft whose movement is managed by the system.
    AircraftCharacteristics
    Stores information about particular models of aircraft.
    AircraftQueue
    Abstract representation of a queue containing aircraft.
    AircraftType
    Represents the possible types that an aircraft can be.
    AirplaneTerminal
    Represents an airport terminal that is designed to accommodate airplanes.
    AirportCanvas
    Subclass of the JavaFX Canvas to represent the main elements of the airport graphically.
    ControlTower
    Represents a the control tower of an airport.
    ControlTowerInitialiser
    Utility class that contains static methods for loading a control tower and associated entities from files.
    EmergencyState
    Denotes an entity whose behaviour and operations can be affected by emergencies.
    Encodable
    Denotes a class whose state can be encoded and represented as a String.
    FreightAircraft
    Represents an aircraft capable of carrying freight cargo.
    Gate
    Represents an aircraft gate with facilities for a single aircraft to be parked.
    HelicopterTerminal
    Represents an airport terminal that is designed to accommodate helicopters.
    LandingQueue
    Represents a rule-based queue of aircraft waiting in the air to land.
    Launcher
    Entry point for the GUI of the Control Tower Simulation.
    MalformedSaveException
    Exception thrown when a save file is in an invalid format or contains incorrect data.
    NoSpaceException
    Exception thrown when there is insufficient space to undertake an action.
    NoSuitableGateException
    Exception thrown when there is no suitable gate available for an aircraft.
    OccupancyLevel
    Denotes a class that has an inherent capacity and a current level of loading relative to that capacity.
    PassengerAircraft
    Represents an aircraft capable of carrying passenger cargo.
    TakeoffQueue
    Represents a first-in-first-out (FIFO) queue of aircraft waiting to take off.
    Task
    Represents a task currently assigned to an aircraft.
    TaskList
    Represents a circular list of tasks for an aircraft to cycle through.
    TaskType
    Enum to represent the possible types of tasks an aircraft can have.
    Terminal
    Represents an airport terminal building, containing several aircraft gates.
    Tickable
    Denotes a class whose state changes on every tick of the simulation.
    View
    View for the Control Tower Simulation GUI.
    ViewModel
    View model for the Control Tower Simulation GUI.
